    "body": "By the way, I have seen a number of games that handle this just fine by allowing one to make use of the digit-row keys for, e.g. selecting weapons (as in FPS games), without any need to change one's keyboard layout or reassign keyboard shortcuts. If it is possible to implement this approach in OpenRA, this would be the desirable solution.\n"
